## Attribution Requirements

When using this material under the free license, you must include:

1. Credit to "Raymond DePalma" or "AI for the Win"
2. A link to the original repository
3. A link to the CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license
4. Indication of any modifications made

**Example attribution:**

> Based on "AI for the Win" by Raymond DePalma (https://github.com/depalmar/ai_for_the_win), licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0. [Modified from original / Used with modifications / Used as-is].

